title: Picking Records
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

Above the fields tables is a single ''records'' field with a ''Browse'' button.  Click Browse and a modal opens showing the source JSON as a tree.

<$image source="$:/json-convert/images/PickRecordsPath.png" class="screenshot" width="60%" />

Click ''copy'' on the array you want to iterate.  If you click on a specific element (e.g. `[0]`), the picker rewrites that to `[*]` automatically so the records path matches all siblings, not just the one you happened to click on.
